### Get all users (authorized)
GET http://localhost:5113/users
Authorization: Bearer dev-token-123

###

### Create a new user
POST http://localhost:5113/users
Authorization: Bearer dev-token-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}

###

### Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:5113/users/0f510010-f93e-41c1-8880-b0a8951b9b62
Authorization: Bearer dev-token-123

###

### Update user
PUT http://localhost:5113/users/0f510010-f93e-41c1-8880-b0a8951b9b62
Authorization: Bearer dev-token-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "email": "jane.doe@example.com"
}

###

### Delete user
DELETE http://localhost:5113/users/0f510010-f93e-41c1-8880-b0a8951b9b62
Authorization: Bearer dev-token-123

###

### Unauthorized request (should return 401)
GET http://localhost:5113/users

###

### Create user with invalid email (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:5113/users
Authorization: Bearer dev-token-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Invalid",
  "lastName": "Email",
  "email": "not-an-email"
}